snippet.title: Changeling Trailer 2
snippet.description:
Changeling is a non-stat raising, full-length visual novel about love, reconciliation, and trying to survive in a dangerous supernatural world. Play through about 25-35 hours of content and over 40 unique endings while trying to survive the perils of a newly discovered paranormal community. Romance one of 6 love interests as you uncover information about the supernatural and the secrets from your own past - all while you try to patch up your relationship with your twin brother who grows more and more suspicious of you with each passing day.

Demo:
https://steamberry.itch.io/changelingdemo

https://discord.gg/VypBwQ6
